title: Out soon: ‘Bodyguard’ by Bups Saggu
text:
After tasting success in the form of 'Miss kaur' , Bups Saggu is all set to return with 'Bodyguard' , a single featuring Sandy Sandhu and Jotti Dhillon. The lyrics of the song have been penned by Attri and Sangdil 47.
'Bodyguard' will be released by Vyanjhali Records. However, the release date has not been finalised as yet.
Source: Simplybhangra.com
